# Prompt: Revise DEVOS Technical Architecture Document v1.0

You previously produced the **DEVOS Technical Architecture Document v1.0**. That document has been through a Senior Architect review. Below are the **required revisions**, **answered clarification questions**, and **new architectural requirements** that must be incorporated into **v2.0** of the Technical Architecture.

Do NOT produce a diff or summary. Produce the **complete, updated Technical Architecture Document v2.0** incorporating every change below. Where a change conflicts with the current document, the change below takes precedence.

