## SECTION F: Scope Reduction (Redirect Effort)

Defer the following from Phase 3 to Phase 4:
- **TikTok Ads MCP** — Meta is the primary platform. TikTok can reuse 90% of meta-ads-mcp patterns later. (~3-4 days saved)
- **Full Predictive Overrun Engine** — Not enough historical data at Week 7. Ship a simple "burn rate vs remaining budget" calculation in Phase 3, label it "Early Warning". Full predictions in Phase 4. (~3-4 days saved)
- **Contractor Performance Scoring** — No contractors will have enough invoices for meaningful scoring by Week 6. Track raw data now, score later. (~1-2 days saved)
- **Lookalike Audience Builder** — Requires significant confirmed buyer data. At Week 8, sample size is too small. (~1-2 days saved)

Redirect the ~10-15 days saved toward:
- LiteLLM integration and multi-model routing setup
- Agent Engine Worker service deployment
- Messaging channel abstraction
- More thorough RLS testing
- Comprehensive E2E testing

